---
import SEO from '../components/SEO.astro';
import Schema from '../components/Schema.astro';
import LanguageSwitcher from '../components/LanguageSwitcher.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/favicon-32x32.png">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="/favicon-16x16.png">
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="/apple-touch-icon.png">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <!-- SEO Meta Tags -->
    <SEO
        title="About Me - Luís Madeira"
        description="Implementation consultant who executes. I help Portuguese SMEs work smarter through automation and websites."
        locale="en"
    />

    <!-- Structured Data -->
    <Schema type="Organization" />
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Navigation -->
    <nav class="navigation">
        <a href="/" class="logo">luís madeira</a>
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="/#work">Work</a>
            <div class="nav-dropdown">
                <button class="nav-dropdown-toggle">
                    Services
                    <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                        <path d="M7 10L12 15L17 10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                    </svg>
                </button>
                <div class="nav-dropdown-menu">
                    <a href="/consulting">AI Solutions</a>
                    <a href="/services">Websites</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <a href="/about">About</a>
            <a href="/#contact">Contact</a>
            <LanguageSwitcher currentPath="/about" />
        </div>
        <div class="mobile-menu-toggle">
            <span></span>
            <span></span>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="about-hero">
        <div class="about-hero-content">
            <div class="hero-text-section">
                <h1>ABOUT ME</h1>
                <h2>AI consultant who augments teams. I teach SMEs to use AI practically, with existing tools and training that generates fast ROI.</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-image-section">
                <img src="/profile.jpeg" alt="Luís Madeira">
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <section class="content-section">
        <div class="content-container">
            <div class="content-block">
                <h3>Who I Am</h3>
                <p>Originally from Porto, currently pursuing a Master's in Management at IE Business School in Madrid. With 2 years of experience in Venture Capital and a passion for technology, I work with Portuguese SMEs to help them grow smarter.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="content-block">
                <h3>What I Do</h3>
                <p>I'm an AI consultant focused on <strong>augmenting team capacity</strong> in SMEs. I don't sell custom technology — I teach how to use AI tools that already exist (Claude, ChatGPT, Perplexity, etc.) strategically and create processes that work.</p>
                <p>I also create modern websites that rank on Google and convert visitors into customers. Whatever the project, the focus is always the same: practical and measurable results.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="content-block">
                <h3>Approach</h3>
                <p>I work in focused 2-4 week sprints. I start small, test quickly, measure results. I combine practical implementation with team training — the goal is for them to become autonomous, not dependent on me.</p>
                <p>I don't believe in long projects or consultant dependency. If after 8 weeks your team still needs me to use AI, I've failed.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="content-block">
                <h3>Philosophy</h3>
                <p>I believe SMEs don't need to hire expensive specialists or build technology from scratch. The tools already exist — they just need someone to show them how to use them well and train their teams to leverage them.</p>
                <p>My job isn't to create dependency, it's to create autonomy. The faster your team can work without me, the better I've done my job.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="content-block">
                <h3>Why This Focus</h3>
                <p>I started focused on websites and SEO. But I realized many SMEs face a bigger challenge: they don't know how to use AI, they're afraid to invest without guarantees, and teams are too overwhelmed to experiment.</p>
                <p>I saw a clear opportunity: help these companies adopt AI practically, with tools that already exist, training that works, and ROI that's visible quickly. That's what I do now.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="content-block">
                <h3>Values</h3>
                <ul class="values-list">
                    <li><strong>Autonomy, not dependency:</strong> The goal is for the team to become independent as quickly as possible.</li>
                    <li><strong>Existing tools, not custom:</strong> Use what already works instead of reinventing the wheel.</li>
                    <li><strong>Fast ROI:</strong> If you can't see results in 2-4 weeks, something's wrong.</li>
                    <li><strong>Practical training:</strong> Learning by doing, not just theoretical presentations.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="content-block">
                <h3>Background</h3>
                <p><strong>Education:</strong> Pursuing Master's in Management at IE Business School (Madrid). Background in business and technology.</p>
                <p><strong>Experience:</strong> 2 years in Venture Capital, where I learned to evaluate businesses and identify what really matters for growth.</p>
                <p><strong>Location:</strong> Madrid (studies) and Porto (origin). Working remotely with businesses throughout Portugal.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="cta-section">
        <div class="cta-content">
            <h2>Let's Talk?</h2>
            <p>If it makes sense, I'll schedule a 30-minute call to understand your business.</p>
            <div class="cta-links">
                <a href="mailto:luismadeira@ruimadeira.pt" class="cta-button">Send Email</a>
                <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/lumadeira" target="_blank" class="cta-button-secondary">LinkedIn</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <script>
        // Mobile Menu Toggle
        const mobileMenuToggle = document.querySelector('.mobile-menu-toggle');
        const navLinks = document.querySelector('.nav-links');

        if (mobileMenuToggle) {
            mobileMenuToggle.addEventListener('click', () => {
                mobileMenuToggle.classList.toggle('active');
                navLinks.classList.toggle('active');
            });

            // Close menu when clicking on a link
            const links = navLinks.querySelectorAll('a');
            links.forEach(link => {
                link.addEventListener('click', () => {
                    mobileMenuToggle.classList.remove('active');
                    navLinks.classList.remove('active');
                });
            });
        }

        // Dropdown navigation
        const dropdownToggle = document.querySelector('.nav-dropdown-toggle');
        const dropdownMenu = document.querySelector('.nav-dropdown-menu');
        const navDropdown = document.querySelector('.nav-dropdown');

        if (dropdownToggle && dropdownMenu) {
            dropdownToggle.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
                e.stopPropagation();
                navDropdown.classList.toggle('active');
            });

            // Close dropdown when clicking outside
            document.addEventListener('click', () => {
                navDropdown.classList.remove('active');
            });

            navDropdown.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
                e.stopPropagation();
            });
        }
    </script>

    <Footer locale="en" />
</body>
</html>

<style>
/* Reset & Base Styles */
* {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
}

:root {
    --color-bg: #0d0d0d;
    --color-text: #c7c7c7;
    --color-accent: #d3e97a;
    --color-dark: #1a1a1a;
    --font-primary: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    --font-heading: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
}

body {
    font-family: var(--font-primary);
    background-color: var(--color-bg);
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.6;
    overflow-x: hidden;
}

/* Navigation */
.navigation {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 24px 60px;
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    background-color: var(--color-bg);
    z-index: 1000;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
}

.logo {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 32px;
    letter-spacing: -0.32px;
    color: var(--color-text);
    text-decoration: none;
}

.nav-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 32px;
    align-items: center;
}

.nav-links a {
    color: var(--color-text);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.48px;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
}

.nav-links a:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent);
}

/* Dropdown Navigation */
.nav-dropdown {
    position: relative;
}

.nav-dropdown-toggle {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.48px;
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-primary);
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
}

.nav-dropdown-toggle:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent);
}

.nav-dropdown-toggle svg {
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
}

.nav-dropdown.active .nav-dropdown-toggle svg {
    transform: rotate(180deg);
}

.nav-dropdown-menu {
    position: absolute;
    top: calc(100% + 16px);
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    background-color: var(--color-dark);
    border: 1px solid #333;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 8px;
    min-width: 160px;
    opacity: 0;
    visibility: hidden;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease, visibility 0.3s ease;
    z-index: 1000;
}

.nav-dropdown.active .nav-dropdown-menu {
    opacity: 1;
    visibility: visible;
}

.nav-dropdown-menu a {
    display: block;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    color: var(--color-text);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 15px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    transition: background-color 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease;
}

.nav-dropdown-menu a:hover {
    background-color: rgba(211, 233, 122, 0.1);
    color: var(--color-accent);
}

.mobile-menu-toggle {
    display: none;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
    cursor: pointer;
}

.mobile-menu-toggle span {
    width: 32px;
    height: 2px;
    background-color: var(--color-text);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

/* About Hero */
.about-hero {
    padding: 80px 108px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #333;
}

.about-hero-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: center;
}

.hero-text-section h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 76px;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.76px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
}

.hero-text-section h2 {
    font-size: 28px;
    line-height: 1.4;
    font-weight: 500;
    opacity: 0.95;
}

.hero-image-section {
    width: 100%;
    height: 500px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background-color: var(--color-dark);
}

.hero-image-section img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
}

/* Content Section */
.content-section {
    padding: 80px 108px;
}

.content-container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
}

.content-block {
    margin-bottom: 64px;
}

.content-block:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
}

.content-block h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 32px;
    letter-spacing: -0.32px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    color: var(--color-text);
}

.content-block p {
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    opacity: 0.95;
}

.content-block p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
}

.values-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
}

.values-list li {
    padding-left: 32px;
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    opacity: 0.95;
}

.values-list li::before {
    content: '→';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 20px;
}

/* CTA Section */
.cta-section {
    padding: 120px 108px;
    border-top: 1px solid #333;
    text-align: center;
}

.cta-content {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
}

.cta-content h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 64px;
    letter-spacing: -0.64px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
}

.cta-content p {
    font-size: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    opacity: 0.9;
}

.cta-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.cta-button {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: var(--color-accent);
    color: var(--color-bg);
    padding: 16px 40px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 16px;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, background-color 0.2s ease;
}

.cta-button:hover {
    background-color: #c5db6f;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
}

.cta-button-secondary {
    display: inline-block;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    padding: 16px 40px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-accent);
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 16px;
    transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
}

.cta-button-secondary:hover {
    background-color: rgba(211, 233, 122, 0.1);
}

/* Responsive Design */
@media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .navigation {
        padding: 24px 32px;
    }

    .about-hero {
        padding: 60px 32px;
    }

    .about-hero-content {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 48px;
    }

    .hero-image-section {
        max-width: 500px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .content-section {
        padding: 60px 32px;
    }

    .cta-section {
        padding: 80px 32px;
    }
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
    .navigation {
        padding: 20px 16px;
    }

    .logo {
        font-size: 28px;
    }

    .nav-links {
        position: fixed;
        top: 76px;
        right: -100%;
        width: 100%;
        height: calc(100vh - 76px);
        background-color: var(--color-bg);
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: flex-start;
        padding: 40px 0;
        transition: right 0.3s ease;
        border-top: 1px solid #333;
    }

    .nav-links.active {
        right: 0;
    }

    .nav-links a {
        font-size: 24px;
    }

    .nav-dropdown-toggle {
        font-size: 24px;
    }

    .nav-dropdown-menu {
        position: static;
        transform: none;
        margin-top: 16px;
        border: none;
        background-color: transparent;
        padding: 0;
    }

    .nav-dropdown.active .nav-dropdown-menu {
        display: block;
    }

    .nav-dropdown-menu:not(.active) {
        display: none;
    }

    .nav-dropdown-menu a {
        font-size: 20px;
        padding: 12px 0;
    }

    .mobile-menu-toggle {
        display: flex;
    }

    .mobile-menu-toggle.active span:first-child {
        transform: rotate(45deg) translate(8px, 8px);
    }

    .mobile-menu-toggle.active span:last-child {
        transform: rotate(-45deg) translate(8px, -8px);
    }

    .about-hero {
        padding: 60px 16px;
    }

    .hero-text-section h1 {
        font-size: 48px;
    }

    .hero-text-section h2 {
        font-size: 22px;
    }

    .hero-image-section {
        height: 400px;
    }

    .content-section {
        padding: 40px 16px;
    }

    .content-block h3 {
        font-size: 28px;
    }

    .cta-section {
        padding: 60px 16px;
    }

    .cta-content h2 {
        font-size: 48px;
    }

    .cta-content p {
        font-size: 18px;
    }

    .cta-links {
        flex-direction: column;
    }

    .cta-button,
    .cta-button-secondary {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 300px;
    }
}
</style>
